            Hi there!
            I am a data programmer and analyst living in Seattle. I work with the Puget Sound Regional Council (PSRC) as part of their data science team working on general automation projects, dashboard building, and promoting R. When not dabbling in code, I’m catching up on the latest K-drama and improving my chocolate chip cookie baking skills.
            
            Education
            Certificate in Front-end Development
            University of Washington Professional and Continuing Education, 2020
            BA in Geography
            University of Washington, 2007
